create or alter view  moves
as
select *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'silver/moves',
        data_source = 'cmsa',
        FORMAT = 'DELTA'
    ) AS [moves]

26078
select DATEPART(Day,Move_Time) as date$,  sum(BayChange) from rtg_baychange where DATEPART( year, move_time)=2023 and DATEPART(week,Move_Time) in (8 )
 and datepart(month,Move_Time)=2 and Category_Id in ('EXPRT','IMPRT')
and (Prev_Position not like 'T-%' or Position_Name not LIKE 'T-%') and Move_Time is not null  group by DATEPART(Day,Move_Time)
order by 1
